# NETWORK::NETWORK_HAS_FOLLOW_INVITE

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Follow invite actions. These are invites sent by someone who has tagged the local player
as a 'follower'.
